        <title>海美迪 H7三代 电视盒子调教</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/himedi-h7/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 18 Sep 2015 13:08:23 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/himedi-h7/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;小米盒子用着越来越不爽了，播放 1080P 或者高码率 720P 带 DTS 音轨的电影时音频经常卡顿，暂停跳进度条也很卡，双核 A9 也该淘汰了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最不能忍的是启动时竟然有广告，偶尔还推送广告，连屏保都是广告！ROOT 了禁用自带的启动器用第三方启动器，还不能设置壁纸！WTF！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;反正是不会再考虑小米的东西，前段时间和朋友买了个海美迪的 H7 二代，感觉还不错，遥控器还能切换鼠标模式。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;现在这家伙出了三代，处理器升级到了瑞芯微的64位八核 RK3368 ，当然，是那种大小核心的架构，八个核心不会同时开启，不过四个 A57 核心同时开启应该还是很给力的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;颜色挺土鳖的，带一条天线看起来有点像路由器，不过并不支持 802.11ac （5GHz）WIFI ，当然我都是用有线连接的，速度稳定。&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-1.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-4611&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h7-1&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;853&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-1.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-1-150x100.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;还带着莲花口有点无力吐槽。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;有线网口是百兆的，蓝光原盘的码率大概 50Mbps ，够用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-2.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;853&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h7-2&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4612&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-2.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-2-150x100.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-2-1024x682.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;海美迪 H7 的遥控器密密麻麻的很多按键，小米的简洁很多，另外一个是功放机一个是电视机的遥控。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这遥控是我最满意的地方，它有一个带学习功能电视机控制区，意味着它可以同时开电视机和功放机，淘汰另外两个很大却没什么用的电视机和功放机遥控器，电视机遥控器值用来开电视机，功放机偶尔调节音量，四个学习按键刚好，没有功放机的可以用它来遥控空调！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;底下的数字区可以用来输入密码和设置快捷切换应用，也很好用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;另外，小米的遥控器确认键不能 “暂停 / 播放” MX Player，这点有点奇怪，海美迪的可以，满分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-3.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;960&#34; height=&#34;640&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h7-3&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4613&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-3.jpg 960w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-3-150x100.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-3-300x200.jpg 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202324.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202324.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918202324&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4621&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202324.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202324-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202324-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202324-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最讨厌的默认启动器（桌面），没啥用，而且不能设置第三方启动器为默认启动器，需要 ROOT 后用钛备份冻结掉它默认启动器才能更改。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918200508.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918200508.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918200508&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4614&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918200508.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918200508-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918200508-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918200508-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;自带的媒体中心，不能自动匹配字幕有点可惜，其他功能都有。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201308.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201308.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918201308&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4615&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201308.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201308-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201308-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201308-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Android 5.1.1 ，很原生，Lollipop 的彩蛋都有。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201332.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201332.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918201332&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4616&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201332.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201332-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201332-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201332-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5.1 声道音响系统的需要设置 HDMI 音频源码输出，由功放机解码。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201344.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201344.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918201344&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4617&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201344.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201344-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201344-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201344-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;用了第三方启动器（Nova Launcher）就不能打开海美迪的媒体中心了，因为找不到快捷方式。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;但是第三方启动器比自带的好看多了，能设置壁纸，添加自己喜欢的小部件，遥控器操作也没问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201415.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201415.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918201415&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4618&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201415.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201415-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201415-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201415-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;通过 DS Video 和 MX Player 来播放和管理 NAS 的电影/剧集，可以通过射手的 API 匹配字幕。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201525.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201525.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918201525&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4619&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201525.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201525-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201525-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918201525-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;以前的 XBMC 多媒体中心，功能超级强大，但是我这里输出 5.1 声道音频的时候超级卡不知为何，放置 Play 。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202055.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202055.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h720150918202055&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4620&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202055.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202055-150x84.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202055-300x169.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h720150918202055-1024x576.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;可通过 &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.4k123.com/thread-12403-1-1.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;TV盒子工具&lt;/a&gt; 进行 ROOT ，先用 &lt;a href=&#34;http://bbs.himedia.cn/thread-185029-1-1.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Adb工具&lt;/a&gt; 开启 Adb ，然后通过 TCP 连接到电视盒进行一键 ROOT 操作，傻瓜式的。之后就慢慢折腾吧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-ROOT.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;894&#34; height=&#34;715&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-ROOT.png&#34; alt=&#34;himedi-h7-ROOT&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4622&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-ROOT.png 894w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-ROOT-150x120.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/himedi-h7-ROOT-300x240.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 894px) 100vw, 894px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4K 啊什么的就不测试了，毕竟电视都是 1080P 的，4K 的片源也找不到，反正盒子性能很强大，应用切换播放暂停拉进度条什么的都反应快速。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;比较硬伤的是，海美迪的关机真的是关机，所以每次打开盒子都要开机，设置成休眠会死啊…另外关机还是开机的指示灯都闪瞎狗眼…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;瑕不掩瑜，性能无可挑剔，很好用电视盒子。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;小米盒子吃屎去吧&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3%e7%9b%92%e5%ad%90%e5%90%83%e5%b1%8e%e5%8e%bb%e5%90%a7&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;小米盒子吃屎去吧！&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
